<div class="content">
	<p>This page describes how to post news using the <a href="#apps/topic-viewer">News Browser</a> app.  You can post messages, comments to other posts, replies to other people's comments, image galleries, and even files and folders. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-newspaper"></i>Posting Messages</h2>
			<p>To post a messsage, simply type in you message in the content area labelled "What's New".  When you're ready to post your message, hit the "Post" button. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/new-post.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Posting a Message</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-grin"></i>Adding Emoji</h2>
			<p>To add an emoji to your message, click on the first button underneath the message box. Note: emoji will look slightly different depending upon the platform / operating system that you are on. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/adding-emoji.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Adding Emoji</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-comment"></i>Adding Comments</h2>
			<p>To comment on an existing post, just click the "Comment" button to the lower right of the message. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/comment-button.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Comment Button</div>
			</div>

			<p>This will open up the comments panel, where you can add messages and image or file attachments. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/comments-panel.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Comments Panel</div>
			</div>

			<p>Your comment will be shown in a comment bubble inside the comments panel. Also, note that a comment badge will be shown in the post header indicating the total number of comments to this post. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/posted-comment.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Posted Comment</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-reply"></i>Replying to Comments</h2>
			<p>To reply to a comment, just click on the "Reply" button to the lower right of the comment message. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/reply-button.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Reply Button</div>
			</div>

			<p>This will open up the reply panel, where you can add messages and image or file attachments. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/reply-panel.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Reply Panel</div>
			</div>

			<p>Your reply will be shown underneath the comment that you replied to. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-news/posting-news/posted-reply.png" /></a>
				<div class="caption">Posted Reply</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>